        "body": "<p>As @Gagravarr mentioned in comment, this is not a <code>Tika<\/code> slowness, since <code>Tesseract<\/code> is CPU consuming process. <\/p>\n\n<p>To handle it, I have separated this process on another server, using <code>FIFO<\/code> method. So that only one file is processed at a time.<\/p>\n",
